headline.main: NEW FROM EUROPE.; Alleged Treaty of Commerce between Austria and the United States. THE CONFERENCES. ARRIVAL OF THE FULTON. OUT PARIS CORRESPONDENCE. Preparations for the Imperial Birth. OUR PARIS CORRESPONDENCE.

docs.lead_paragraph: The United States Mail Steamship Fulton, Capt. WOTTON, arrived at this port, on Saturday morning, from Havre and Southampton, bringing London dates to the afternoon of the 12th March. Her news is one day later than by the Emeu, but not so late, by two days, as the telegraphic intelligence from Halifax, per Canada.

docs.lead_paragraph: [Advertisement.] Diseases of the Lungs--Notice. Dr. ROBERT HUNTER begs to inform his patients in Philadelphia that he has opened an establishment in that city under the professional charge of Dr. F. MORSON, for the special treatment of diseases of the throat and lungs.
